</script></section></div><div class="dynamic-layouts-container-column layout-builder--layout__region col-lg-4 "><section class="block block-block-content block-block-content98aa017d-8202-43e5-8a04-d4931c7e83ed clearfix"><div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"><aside id="ad-sidebar-atf"> </aside></div></section><section class="most-popular content-rec-target block block-views block-views-blockmost-popular-block-1 clearfix"><div class="views-element-container"><div class="mostPopularListing view view-most-popular view-id-most_popular view-display-id-block_1 js-view-dom-id-bc1f80fa5cb01b2f9ca091d153ade523feeca25d949836a0dbc6de2a008ca25c"><div class="view-header"><div class="blockHeading"><h2>Most popular</h2><div class="headingBarWrapper"><div class="cornerLeftBottom"></div><div class="cornerRightTop"></div><div class="headingBar"></div></div></div></div><div class="view-content"><div class="lsitingRow"><div class="listingNumber">1</div><div class="listingContent"><div class="listingTitle"><a href="/arts-culture/2024/05/03/merton-huxley-lsd-mysticism-247675" hreflang="en">Why Thomas Merton was suspicious of psychedelic drugs </a></div><div class="byAuthor">Colm O’Shea</div></div></div><div class="lsitingRow"><div class="listingNumber">2</div><div class="listingContent"><div class="listingTitle"><a href="/faith/2024/05/03/pope-francis-universities-education-liberal-247859" hreflang="en">Pope Francis laments American universities that are ‘too liberal’ and ‘only train technicians’</a></div><div class="byAuthor">Justin McLellan – Catholic News Service</div></div></div><div class="lsitingRow"><div class="listingNumber">3</div><div class="listingContent"><div class="listingTitle"><a href="/arts-culture/2024/05/03/philomena-catholic-movie-club-247851" hreflang="en">‘Philomena’ asks: In the shadow of the church’s abuse, why do Catholics stay?</a></div><div class="byAuthor">John Dougherty</div></